License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Justin Ethier
Maintainer:          Justin Ethier <github.com/justinethier>
Homepage:            http://justinethier.github.com/husk-scheme
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.8
Build-Type:          Simple
Category:            Compilers/Interpreters, Language
